{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_33","type":"agent_message","text":"The current migration head is confirmed as `0010_operational_recovery`. The key behavioral detail is the strict SQL predicate `lease_expires_at < now`; I’ll preserve that exactly in both adapters (including the boundary instant), while `is_claim_live` remains `lease_expires_at > now`. Claims will lazily insert the `(plan_id, goal_id)` row and conditionally update it in one committed transaction."}}
